room_title: Escape room "Bomb Squad" by Escape the Space in Athens
room_description: Have you ever wondered if you would have what it takes to be a part of the country’s most elite Bomb Squad? Wonder no more. This room will challenge your skills... as you, and your team, battle against our city’s most notorious villain! Determined to destroy our city, you are the only thing that could possibly stop him... and his bombs!
